{"tid":1791190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國下議院通過首相莊漢生的脫歐協議草案","createTime":"2019-12-20T14:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T15:57:57.000Z","uid":35221,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d9376d5986c65da027c71ad21f998cb81be677","tid":1791190,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IBywZtbK2SA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIBywZtbK2SA&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=cf606767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IBywZtbK2SA</a>"},{"pid":"2fb6332e8f4da9bd662d5a4c80045fbd6332c498","tid":1791190,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"Brexit: MPs back Boris Johnson's bill<br />\n<br />\nMPs have backed Prime Minister Boris Johnson's plan for the UK to leave the EU on 31 January.<br />\n<br />\nThey voted 358 to 234 in favour of the EU (Withdrawal Agreement) Bill, which now goes on to further scrutiny in the House of Commons and House of Lords.<br />\n<br />\nThe bill would also ban an extension of the transition period - during which the UK is out of the EU but follows many of its rules - past 2020.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier, Boris Johnson argued that it would allow the UK to &quot;move forward&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nLabour leader Jeremy Corbyn told his MPs to vote against it, saying there was &quot;a better and fairer way&quot; to leave the EU.<br />\n<br />\nMPs are now voting on the programme motion, which sets out the timetable for further debate on the bill over three days - 7, 8 and 9 January.<br />\n<br />\nThe government says it will get the bill into law in time for the 31 January Brexit deadline.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-50870939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-50870939&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=2b59ad9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-50870939&h=b78b3c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-50870939</a>"},{"pid":"8ae2cf1c46afcfa7536e96300410957c435972d2","tid":1791190,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"即係成功脫歐?"},{"pid":"696932f0f8e2ce60b2c4482f6c255692e9c36f8f","tid":1791190,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"上議院呢?"},{"pid":"bb345a6bc35fc7975c9aed65df1d83c1caa094a1","tid":1791190,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"上議院過硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adc8f33cc824dba4155c0842f6ee0cf3fca7e9a","tid":1791190,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"696932f0f8e2ce60b2c4482f6c255692e9c36f8f","tid":1791190,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"上議院呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"啱啱終於過下議院咋，拖鳩咗三年"},{"pid":"9a6feff21fe8f20ddd0702f818396367af6417ca","tid":1791190,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696932f0f8e2ce60b2c4482f6c255692e9c36f8f","tid":1791190,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"上議院呢?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"上議院就算9數，下議院權力大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞掂脫歐係時候make British great again"},{"pid":"1f9500e15fdc9ed866e5044b9260e5bd4240fc47","tid":1791190,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a6feff21fe8f20ddd0702f818396367af6417ca","tid":179119